hopobject.body: I'm originally from Dublin but now live in Edinburgh intelimax iq preo In “The Best of Us,” a group of friends from college go on vacation together, and money also plays a role, in part because it shows the differences in the couples. Everyone started on even footing in college, and then when they united for a 35th birthday party, everyone had gone in wildly different directions. One has four kids, another is struggling with infertility, one is wildly successful and there are lots of opportunities for conflict.
